			<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">Bipolar disorder</h1>
									<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
									<div id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
								<div id="contentSub"></div>
												<div id="jump-to-nav" class="mw-jump">
					Jump to:					<a href="#mw-head">navigation</a>, 					<a href="#p-search">search</a>
				</div>
				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="hatnote">"Manic depression" redirects here. For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Manic_depression_(disambiguation)" title="Manic depression (disambiguation)" class="mw-disambig">Manic depression (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<div class="hatnote">"Bipolar disorders" redirects here. For the medical journal, see <a href="/wiki/Bipolar_Disorders_(journal)" title="Bipolar Disorders (journal)">Bipolar Disorders (journal)</a>.</div>
